parameters.name: AttachmentKey
parameters.description: The key of an attachment that is returned after the attachment is uploaded. You can call the [GetUserUploadFileJob](~~206069~~) operation to query the key of the attachment.

parameters.name: Tid
parameters.description:
The ID of the tenant.

>  To view the tenant ID, move the pointer over the profile picture in the upper-right corner of the DMS console. For more information, see [Manage DMS tenants](~~181330~~).
